TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TV.CORP_CD CORP_OWNR_ID , TSD.LAST_ALOC_TS ACTVY_TS , TSD.CREATE_USER_ID ACTVY_USR_ID , TQ.PERIOD_ID ACTVY_PRD_ID , TQ.HVST_ID ACTVY_SRC_OBJ_ID ,TH.HRCY_NM ,VR.RPT_TITLE ,TQ.RPT_ID ,TQ.ADMN_DISCNT_AMT , TQ.BASE_DISCNT_AMT ,TQ.CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT , TQ.FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT , TQ.PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT , TQ.PRFMC_DISCNT_AMT , VR.CO_BE_ID ACTVY_BUS_ENTY_ID , VR.VNDR_ID ACTVY_VNDR_ID FROM VRAP.THARVEST_QUE TQ INNER JOIN ( SELECT DISTINCT SD.SNAP_ID , SD.HVST_ID , SD.CREATE_TS , MAX(SD.LAST_ALOC_TS) LAST_ALOC_TS , MIN(SD.CREATE_USER_ID) CREATE_USER_ID FROM VRAP.TSNAP_DTL SD GROUP BY SD.SNAP_ID , SD.HVST_ID , SD.CREATE_TS) TSD ON TQ.HVST_ID = TSD.HVST_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TSNAP TS ON TSD.SNAP_ID = TS.SNAP_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.VREPORT VR ON TQ.RPT_ID = VR.RPT_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.THIERARCHY TH ON VR.HRCY_ID = TH.HRCY_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TCNTRCT TC ON TH.CNTRCT_ID = TC.CNTRCT_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TVNDR TV ON TC.VNDR_ID = TV.VNDR_ID WHERE TQ.HVST_STAT_CD = 2 --HARVEST COMPLETED AND TS.SNAP_SEQ_NB = -1 AND TSD.CREATE_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_AllocationAllocate') WITH UR

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Hold SUM of multiple fields coming from Sub-query
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: ACTVY_VAL_AT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TV.CORP_CD CORP_OWNR_ID , TADD.APRV_ACTN_CD , TADD.APRV_RECV_TS ACTVY_TS , TU.USER_GID , TRH.RBAT_RPT_PRD_ID ACTVY_PRD_ID , TRH.RECN_GID ACTVY_SRC_OBJ_ID , TV.VNDR_NM , TRC.CD_NM , TADD.APRV_ROLE_CD , DS_VAL.DSTR_VAL ACTVY_VAL_AT , TRH.CO_BE_ID ACTVY_BUS_ENTY_ID , TRH.VEND_ID ACTVY_VNDR_ID FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_HDR TRH INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR TDH ON TRH.RECN_GID = TDH.RECN_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL TADD ON TDH.DSTR_GID = TADD.DSTR_GID LEFT JOIN VRAP.TUSER TU ON UPPER(TRIM(TADD.APRV_RECV_USER_ID)) = UPPER(TRIM(TU.LDAP_ID)) INNER JOIN VRAP.TVNDR TV ON TRH.VEND_ID = TV.VNDR_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.TVNDR_REBT_CD TRC ON TRH.CO_BE_ID = TRC.CD_NB AND TRC.TYP_CD = 80 INNER JOIN ( SELECT DS.DSTR_GID , SUM(COALESCE(DS.ADMN_PRIR_DSTR_AMT +DS.ADMN_PEND_DSTR_AMT +DS.BASE_PRIR_DSTR_AMT +DS.BASE_PEND_DSTR_AMT +DS.PERF_PRIR_DSTR_AMT +DS.PERF_PEND_DSTR_AMT +DS.FRMLY_PRIR_DSTR_AMT +DS.FRMLY_PEND_DSTR_AMT +DS.CTRC_PRIR_DSTR_AMT +DS.CTRC_PEND_DSTR_AMT +DS.PRC_PTCT_PRIR_DSTR_AMT +DS.PRC_PTCT_PEND_DSTR_AMT,0)) DSTR_VAL FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_SUMM DS GROUP BY DS.DSTR_GID ) DS_VAL ON DS_VAL.DSTR_GID = TDH.DSTR_GID WHERE TADD.APRV_ACTN_CD IN (3,4) AND TADD.APRV_ROLE_CD != 5 AND DATE(TADD.APRV_RECV_TS) > '$$LOAD_LAST_TS' WITH UR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TV.CORP_CD CORP_OWNR_ID , TRRMIH.HIST_INSRT_TS , TRRMIH.LAST_UPDT_USER_ID ACTVY_USR_ID , TRRMIH.RBAT_RPT_PRD_ID ACTVY_PRD_ID , TRRMIH.VEND_ID ACTVY_SRC_OBJ_ID , TRRMIH.INV_TITL_TXT ACTVY_SRC_TITLE_TX , TRRMIH.INV_TOT_AMT ACTVY_VAL_AT , TRRMIH.CO_BE_ID ACTVY_BUS_ENTY_ID FROM VRAP.RCNH_RBAT_MFG_INV_HDR TRRMIH INNER JOIN ( SELECT HIH.INV_ID , MIN(HIH.HIST_INSRT_TS) VOID_TS FROM VRAP.RCNH_RBAT_MFG_INV_HDR HIH WHERE HIH.HIST_INSRT_REAS_CD = 'U' AND HIH.INV_STAT_CD = 2 GROUP BY HIH.INV_ID ) INV_VOID ON INV_VOID.INV_ID = TRRMIH.INV_ID AND INV_VOID.VOID_TS = TRRMIH.HIST_INSRT_TS INNER JOIN VRAP.TVNDR TV ON TRRMIH.VEND_ID = TV.VNDR_ID WHERE TRRMIH.HIST_INSRT_REAS_CD = 'U' AND TRRMIH.INV_STAT_CD = 2 AND TRRMIH.HIST_INSRT_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS_InvoicingVoid') WITH UR
